Package: nitro
Type: Package
Title: Integration of TNT in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tom Brougham
Maintainer: Tom Brougham <tbrougham@paravian.net>
Description: Integration of the phylogenetics software TNT in R. It interfaces
    with a locally installed copy of the TNT command-line program and provides
    functions for performing branch swapping, parsimony ratchet and driven
    (i.e., "New Technology") searches. Each tree search function automatically
    returns a set of trees for visualisation or use with other R packages.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Imports: 
    ape,
    magrittr,
    processx,
    progress
